cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation and labelling. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as the algorithms used for the challenge were fully automated. Additionally, since the data used in the challenge was medical imaging data, it may also belong to the medical informatics (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
